1. Open the [LiveServer](https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=ritwickdey.LiveServer) extension page, click on install, and then VSCode will automatically open and install the extension.

2. Unzip the downloaded project and open the folder using VSCode.

3. In VSCode, right-click on the `_preview.html` file in the root directory and select "open with live server". After the page initialization is completed, you can click on the links on the page to preview.